# 155. |进制转换2

## Question description


将M进制的数X转换为N进制的数输出。


## Solution

Language: **['Java']**

```


import java.util.*;
 
import java.math.*;
 
 
 
public class Main {
 
    public static void main(String[] args) {
 
        Scanner in = new Scanner(System.in);
 
        int m,n;
 
        String x;
 
        m = in.nextInt();
 
        n = in.nextInt();
 
        x = in.next();
 
        BigInteger a = new BigInteger(x,m);
 
        System.out.println(a.toString(n));
 
    }
 
}
```


